OL,4,C'We never knew how dangerous Loch
OL,5,CLomond was'
OL,6, The family of a "one in a million"
OL,7, teenager who drowned in Loch Lomond
OL,8, have pleaded for lessons be be learned
OL,9, from his death.
OL,11,FConnor Markward, 16, lost his life at
OL,12,Fthe beauty spot near Balloch Country
OL,13,FPark three weeks ago.
OL,15,FHe had been enjoying a day out with
OL,16,Ffriends - oblivious to the dangers of
OL,17,Fthe water he was swimming in.
OL,19,FNow his grieving loved ones are calling
OL,20,Ffor a safety campaign in schools to
OL,21,Fprevent a future tragedy.
